//About In the maths type of levels you need to catch correct answers on the questions you can see at the moving player. You lose live catching wrong answer. Player moves to the side where your finger is hold. In the strategy type of levels you need to rationally use your money for buying new characters and power upping existing ones. To defeat all enemies and try not to lose lives. You can click on character you want to buy in the store and put it into the dot in the left side. You can click on the cat to change its specifications. You earn money by defeating enemies. In the time type of levels you need to get to finish in time and also complete some tasks. You can move left and right if you hold your finger on the appropriate side of the screen. To jump you need to swipe your finger up on the screen You can earn new cats by completing levels and use them as players in time levels or strategy levels. Before using cat you need to add it into room. When cat is added you need to choose it. Rooms are needed for using cats you won. Each room has 3 free places. In upcoming game update you will be able to win new rooms for new characters. At the moment there are rooms: Space Base, Laboratory and Moon Sort by attack Sort by price Sort by delay
